RDA agent (person, family, corporate body) properties
has employee
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person employed by the corporate body.
reg:name: employee

rdfs:label: has incumbent
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person holding an office in the corporate body.
reg:name: incumbent

rdfs:label: has sponsor
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person sponsoring the corporate body.
reg:name: sponsor

rdfs:label: has founder
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person who founded the corporate body.
reg:name: founder

rdfs:label: has group member
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a person who is a member of the performing group, expedition, etc.
reg:name: groupMember

rdfs:label: has place associated with the corporate body
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a significant location associated with a corporate body (e.g., location of a conference, etc., location of the headquarters of an organization).
reg:name: placeAssociatedWithTheCorporateBody

rdfs:label: has name of the corporate body
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a word, character, or group of words and/or characters by which a corporate body is known.
reg:name: nameOfTheCorporateBody

rdfs:label: has other designation associated with the corporate body
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to a word, phrase, or abbreviation indicating incorporation or legal status of a corporate body, or any term serving to differentiate the body from other corporate bodies, persons, etc.
reg:name: otherDesignationAssociatedWithTheCorporateBody

rdfs:label: has associated institution
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to an institution commonly associated with a corporate body.
reg:name: associatedInstitution

rdfs:label: has corporate history
skos:definition: Relates a corporate body to historical information about the corporate body.
reg:name: corporateHistory
